timber.log

Interface Timber.Tree

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Timber.TaggedTree
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Timber.DebugTree, Timber.HollowTree
    Enclosing class:
    Timber

    public static interface Timber.Tree
    A facade for handling logging calls. Install instances via Timber.plant(timber.log.Timber.Tree).
